ID: 3
Title:
Activating the ‘Send’ button with the ‘Enter’.

Priority:
Medium

Prerequisites:
N/A

Test type:
Negative (-)

Environment:
Windows 10, Chrome  80.0.3987.149

Description:
Test describes the results of the inability to activate ‘Send’ button with the ‘Enter’ button on keyboard.

Test scenario:
    1.Open the chat.
    2.In the messenger window enter: ‘Hi Nicoletta. I need more info about our task. Could you give me more details?’
    3.Press ‘Enter’ button.
    4.Message has been sent.

The expected results:

    1.The chat is opened.
    2.In the messenger window is entered:  ‘Hi Nicoletta. I need more info about our task. Could you give me more details?’
    3.‘Enter’ button is pressed.
    4.Message has not been sent.
